name.ja: <ruby>騎甲虫<rt>ビートルーパー</rt></ruby>クルーエル・サターン

text.en:
1 "Beetrooper" monster + 1 Insect monster
You cannot Special Summon monsters, except Insect monsters. You can only use each of the following effects of "Beetrooper Cruel Saturn" once per turn. If this card is Special Summoned: You can add 1 "Beetrooper" card from your Deck to your hand. If an Insect monster(s) is banished face-up: You can target 1 of your banished "Beetrooper" monsters; Special Summon it.
